{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775812276196,"sessionID":"ses_28959beedffejL0cu1e0mvWtte","part":{"id":"prt_d76a64ff3001HP48IuMNnqiMlM","messageID":"msg_d76a64201001oVHCMiP44NuU5N","sessionID":"ses_28959beedffejL0cu1e0mvWtte","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_6808e5917ed5410582da5b90","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project structure","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project thoroughly. I need to understand:\n\n1. The overall project structure - find all directories and files\n2. Look specifically at pkg/apis/ directory and any existing code there\n3. Find any design documents, specs, or stage documents (ST-3, ST-4) that describe what needs to be implemented for AR-003\n4. Look for any existing Go code, type definitions, constants, or interfaces\n5. Check for any existing test files\n6. Look at go.mod for module name and dependencies\n7. Find any README, DESIGN.md, or similar documentation\n\nSearch very thoroughly - check all directories, look for .md files, .go files, yaml files, etc. Return ALL findings including file paths and their contents (or summaries of contents).","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_289599e05ffe7JqD5zcWgAg9Zr (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nI have completed a thorough exploration of the agentcube project. Here is the comprehensive report of all findings:\n\n---\n\n## 1. OVERALL PROJECT STRUCTURE\n\n```\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/\n├── .sdd_prompt.md                          # Prompt for generating design.md\n├── changes/\n│   ├── AR-001/                             # CRD AgentRuntime type definition\n│   │   ├── design.md\n│   │   ├── proposal.md\n│   │   └── tasks.md\n│   ├── AR-002/                             # CRD CodeInterpreter type definition\n│   │   ├── delta-spec.md\n│   │   ├── design.md\n│   │   ├── proposal.md\n│   │   └── tasks.md\n│   └── AR-003/                             # CRD shared types and constants (TARGET)\n│       ├── delta-spec.md\n│       ├── design.md\n│       ├── proposal.md\n│       └── tasks.md\n├── ci-cd/\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── cli-toolkit/\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── code-execution/\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── coverage.out                            # Go test coverage output\n├── deployment/\n│   ├── client-go.md                        # Generated client-go library spec\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── design.md                               # AR-003 design document\n├── go.mod                                  # Go module definition\n├── go.sum                                  # Go dependency checksums\n├── idle-cleanup/\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── integrations/\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── pkg/\n│   └── apis/\n│       └── runtime/\n│           └── v1alpha1/                   # ONLY Go source code in project\n│               ├── agent_type.go\n│               ├── agent_type_test.go\n│               ├── codeinterpreter_types.go\n│               ├── codeinterpreter_types_test.go\n│               ├── doc.go\n│               ├── groupversion_info.go\n│               ├── groupversion_info_test.go\n│               ├── register.go\n│               ├── register_test.go\n│               └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go\n├── project.md                              # Project context overview\n├── python-sdk/\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── sandbox-orchestration/\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── session-routing/\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── session-store/\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── test_spec.md                            # TDD specification\n└── testing/\n    └── agentcube_tdd_manifest.md           # TDD manifest\n```\n\n**Key observation:** There is NO `cmd/` directory, NO `Makefile`, NO YAML files, NO `.github/` directory. The only actual Go code lives in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`. All other directories contain only design/spec markdown documents.\n\n---\n\n## 2. go.mod -- Module Name and Dependencies\n\n**File:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/go.mod`\n\n```\nmodule github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n\ngo 1.24.4\n\nrequire (\n    github.com/stretchr/testify v1.11.1\n    k8s.io/api v0.34.1\n    k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1\n    sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.22.2\n)\n```\n\nKey dependencies:\n- `k8s.io/api v0.34.1` -- Kubernetes core API types\n- `k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1` -- Kubernetes apimachinery (schema, metav1, runtime)\n- `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.22.2` -- controller-runtime (scheme.Builder)\n- `github.com/stretchr/testify v1.11.1` -- testing assertions\n\n---\n\n## 3. pkg/apis/ DIRECTORY -- Existing Code\n\n### 3.1 Directory Contents\n\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n\n10 files total:\n- `doc.go` -- Package-level code generation markers\n- `groupversion_info.go` -- GroupVersion, SchemeBuilder, AddToScheme\n- `register.go` -- Kind constants, SchemeGroupVersion alias, Resource() helper\n- `agent_type.go` -- AgentRuntime CRD types\n- `codeinterpreter_types.go` -- CodeInterpreter CRD types + shared types (ProtocolType, AuthModeType, TargetPort)\n- `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` -- Auto-generated DeepCopy methods\n- `agent_type_test.go` -- AgentRuntime tests\n- `codeinterpreter_types_test.go` -- CodeInterpreter + shared type tests\n- `groupversion_info_test.go` -- Scheme registration tests\n- `register_test.go` -- GVK/GVR constant tests\n\n### 3.2 Existing Type Definitions\n\n**In `codeinterpreter_types.go`** (lines 1-82):\n```go\ntype ProtocolType string\n\nconst (\n    ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n    ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n\ntype AuthModeType string\n\nconst (\n    AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n    AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)\n\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    PathPrefix string       `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n    Name       string       `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n    Port       uint32       `json:\"port\"`\n    Protocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreter struct { ... }\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct { ... }\ntype CodeInterpreterStatus struct { ... }\ntype CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct { ... }\ntype CodeInterpreterList struct { ... }\n```\n\n**In `agent_type.go`** (lines 1-51):\n```go\ntype AgentRuntime struct { ... }\ntype AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort     `json:\"targetPort,omitempty\"`\n    Template           *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\"`\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n}\ntype SandboxTemplate struct {\n    Labels      map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n    Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n    Spec        corev1.PodSpec    `json:\"spec\"`\n}\ntype AgentRuntimeStatus struct { ... }\ntype AgentRuntimeList struct { ... }\n```\n\n**In `groupversion_info.go`** (lines 1-14):\n```go\nvar (\n    GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n    SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n    AddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n)\n```\n\n**In `register.go`** (lines 1-22):\n```go\nvar (\n    CodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n    CodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n    CodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n    CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n)\n\nvar (\n    AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n    AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n    AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n)\n\nvar SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n\nfunc Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n    return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n}\n```\n\n**In `doc.go`** (lines 1-3):\n```go\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\npackage v1alpha1\n```\n\n### 3.3 Existing DeepCopy Methods\n\n**In `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`** (324 lines): DeepCopy/DeepCopyInto methods for:\n- `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `SandboxTemplate`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, `AgentRuntimeList`\n- `TargetPort` (simple value-copy, no pointer fields)\n- `CodeInterpreter`, `CodeInterpreterSpec`, `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`, `CodeInterpreterStatus`, `CodeInterpreterList`\n\n---\n\n## 4. AR-003 DESIGN DOCUMENTS\n\n### 4.1 Proposal (`changes/AR-003/proposal.md`)\n\n**Title:** AR-003: CRD Shared Types and Constants\n\n**Purpose:** Extract shared types (`TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`, `AuthModeType`) from `codeinterpreter_types.go` into a dedicated `shared_types.go` file.\n\n**Key decisions:**\n- Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` with all shared types\n- Remove `ProtocolType`, `AuthModeType`, `TargetPort` from `codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- `agent_type.go` needs no changes (same-package reference)\n- Create `shared_types_test.go` for unit tests\n\n**Shared types to extract:**\n```\nshared_types.go\n├── ProtocolType (string enum)\n│   ├── ProtocolTypeHTTP  = \"HTTP\"\n│   └── ProtocolTypeHTTPS = \"HTTPS\"\n├── AuthModeType (string enum)\n│   ├── AuthModePicoD = \"picod\"\n│   └── AuthModeNone  = \"none\"\n└── TargetPort (struct)\n    ├── pathPrefix: string (optional)\n    ├── name: string (optional)\n    ├── port: uint32 (required)\n    └── protocol: ProtocolType\n```\n\n### 4.2 Design Document (`changes/AR-003/design.md`)\n\nThis is the most detailed document (268 lines). It proposes a **slightly different** file structure than the proposal:\n\n**Proposed file structure (design.md):**\n```\npkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n├── doc.go                        # unchanged\n├── groupversion_info.go          # MERGE: absorb SchemeGroupVersion + Resource() from register.go\n├── types.go                      # NEW: shared types (TargetPort, ProtocolType)\n├── constants.go                  # NEW: shared constants (well-known annotation keys)\n├── agent_type.go                 # no changes needed\n├── codeinterpreter_types.go      # remove ProtocolType, TargetPort; keep AuthModeType + CRD types\n├── register.go                   # DELETE: merged into groupversion_info.go\n├── zz_generated.deepcopy.go      # regenerated\n└── *_test.go                     # updated\n```\n\n**New `types.go` content:**\n```go\npackage v1alpha1\n\ntype ProtocolType string\n\nconst (\n    ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n    ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    PathPrefix string       `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n    Name       string       `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n    Port       uint32       `json:\"port\"`\n    Protocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n}\n```\n\n**New `constants.go` content:**\n```go\npackage v1alpha1\n\nconst (\n    AnnotationKeyRuntime = \"agentcube.io/runtime\"\n    AnnotationKeyVersion = \"agentcube.io/version\"\n)\n```\n\n**Modified `groupversion_info.go`** (absorbs register.go):\n```go\nvar (\n    GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n    SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion  // alias for backward compat\n    SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n    AddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n)\n\nfunc Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n    return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n}\n\n// Kind constants for both CRDs\nvar (\n    CodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n    CodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n    CodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n    CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n\n    AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n    AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n    AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n)\n```\n\n### 4.3 Delta Spec (`changes/AR-003/delta-spec.md`)\n\nContains Gherkin-style requirements (149 lines). Key requirements:\n\n1. **ProtocolType enumeration** -- typed string with HTTP/HTTPS values\n2. **AuthModeType enumeration** -- typed string with picod/none values\n3. **TargetPort struct** -- with correct JSON tags, omitempty behavior, Port as required field\n4. **Single source of truth** -- exactly one definition of each shared type\n5. **DeepCopy generation** -- TargetPort must have DeepCopy/DeepCopyInto in zz_generated.deepcopy.go\n6. **Build and test integrity** -- `go build ./pkg/apis/...` must pass, all tests must pass\n7. **GroupVersion and SchemeBuilder** -- correct group, version, scheme registration\n8. **Kind and GroupVersionKind constants** -- correct values for both CRDs\n\n### 4.4 Tasks (`changes/AR-003/tasks.md`)\n\nStage: ST-1 (Proposal). 5 task groups:\n\n- **T-001:** Create `shared_types.go` with ProtocolType, AuthModeType, TargetPort (7 subtasks)\n- **T-002:** Unit tests for constant values (3 subtasks)\n- **T-003:** Unit tests for TargetPort zero-value and full-field tests (2 subtasks)\n- **T-004:** Generate DeepCopy methods via `make generate` (3 subtasks)\n- **T-005:** Full validation gate (5 subtasks)\n\n---\n\n## 5. EXISTING TEST FILES\n\n### 5.1 `codeinterpreter_types_test.go` (724 lines)\n\nComprehensive tests including:\n- `TestProtocolTypeConstants` -- verifies HTTP/HTTPS values\n- `TestAuthModeTypeConstants` -- verifies picod/none values\n- `TestTargetPortDefaults` -- zero-value behavior\n- `TestTargetPortWithAllFields` -- full field assignment\n- `TestTargetPortDeepCopy` -- copy isolation\n- `TestCodeInterpreterSpecDefaults` -- default values\n- `TestCodeInterpreterDeepCopy` -- full DeepCopy isolation\n- `TestCodeInterpreterListDeepCopy` -- list DeepCopy\n- `TestCodeInterpreterStatusDefaults` -- status zero values\n- Many more DeepCopy isolation tests for all types\n- `TestProtocolTypeAsString`, `TestAuthModeTypeAsString` -- string conversion tests\n\n### 5.2 `agent_type_test.go` (235 lines)\n\nTests including:\n- `TestAgentRuntimeDefaultValues` -- nil/empty defaults\n- `TestAgentRuntimeDeepCopy` -- DeepCopy isolation\n- `TestAgentRuntimeListDeepCopy` -- list DeepCopy\n- `TestSandboxTemplateDeepCopy` -- template DeepCopy\n- `TestAgentRuntimeSpecDeepCopy` -- spec DeepCopy\n- `TestAgentRuntimeStatusDeepCopy` -- status DeepCopy\n- `TestAgentRuntimeWithNilTemplate` -- nil template handling\n- `TestAgentRuntimeWithEmptyPorts` -- empty ports\n- `TestAgentRuntimeWithAllFields` -- all fields populated\n\n### 5.3 `register_test.go` (47 lines)\n\nTests including:\n- `TestGroupVersionConstants` -- Group, Version, AgentRuntimeKind, Resource()\n- `TestCodeInterpreterGroupVersionConstants` -- CodeInterpreter Kind constants\n- `TestAgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind` -- AgentRuntime GVK\n- `TestSchemeGroupVersionAlias` -- SchemeGroupVersion == GroupVersion\n- `TestResourceHelper` -- Resource() for agentruntimes and codeinterpreters\n\n### 5.4 `groupversion_info_test.go` (40 lines)\n\nTests including:\n- `TestSchemeRegistration` -- AgentRuntime and AgentRuntimeList scheme registration\n- `TestCodeInterpreterSchemeRegistration` -- CodeInterpreter and CodeInterpreterList scheme registration\n\n---\n\n## 6. KEY OBSERVATIONS ABOUT AR-003 IMPLEMENTATION\n\n### Discrepancy Between Proposal and Design\n\nThe **proposal.md** says to create `shared_types.go`, while **design.md** says to create `types.go` and `constants.go` as separate files, and also proposes merging `register.go` into `groupversion_info.go` and deleting `register.go`.\n\nThe **tasks.md** references `shared_types.go` (matching the proposal), not `types.go` + `constants.go` (matching the design).\n\n### What Currently Exists vs. What AR-003 Requires\n\n| Item | Current Location | AR-003 Target |\n|------|-----------------|---------------|\n| `ProtocolType` type + constants | `codeinterpreter_types.go` | New shared file |\n| `AuthModeType` type + constants | `codeinterpreter_types.go` | New shared file |\n| `TargetPort` struct | `codeinterpreter_types.go` | New shared file |\n| Kind constants | `register.go` | Merge into `groupversion_info.go` |\n| `SchemeGroupVersion` alias | `register.go` | Merge into `groupversion_info.go` |\n| `Resource()` helper | `register.go` | Merge into `groupversion_info.go` |\n| `register.go` | Exists | DELETE |\n| `shared_types.go` / `types.go` | Does NOT exist | CREATE |\n| `constants.go` | Does NOT exist | CREATE (per design.md) |\n| `shared_types_test.go` / `types_test.go` | Does NOT exist | CREATE |\n| `constants_test.go` | Does NOT exist | CREATE (per design.md) |\n\n### Existing tests that will need updating\n\n- `register_test.go` -- will need to be renamed/merged into `groupversion_info_test.go` if `register.go` is deleted\n- `codeinterpreter_types_test.go` -- currently tests ProtocolType, AuthModeType, TargetPort; these tests will still work since they are same-package, but the types will be defined in a different file\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_289599e05ffe7JqD5zcWgAg9Zr","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775812108791,"end":1775812276193}}}}
